description: Lists versions for the specified application.

parameters.name: ApplicationId
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the application.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token to request the next page of results.

nested_items.name: Versions
nested_items.description: An array of version summaries for the application.

nested_items.name: CreationTime
nested_items.description: The date and time this resource was created.

nested_items.name: SemanticVersion
nested_items.description: The semantic version of the application:

nested_items.name: SourceCodeUrl
nested_items.description: A link to a public repository for the source code of your application, for example the URL of a specific GitHub commit.
